---
title: Quick Mexican Beef Loaded Nachos with Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: Quick grab the sour cream, and those crunch corn chips, don’t forget the all-important charred corn salsa with
tomato and herbs, we’re going to need it to build the best nachos imaginable. Beef mince cooked in enchilada
sauce is a must-have to bring everything together. Now dig in before it’s all gone.

